Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:22.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:27.50,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:29.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:34.49,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:37.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:39.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:47.89,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:55.51,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:57.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:02:00.76,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:05.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:11.51,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:16.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:23.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:28.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:33.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:39.01,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:44.03,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:22.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛說愛「過於沉重」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:27.50,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在轉變成恨之前　把它拒絕於心門之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:29.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬物皆是如此吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:34.49,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是把不合時宜的事隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:37.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是冒牌貨的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:39.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在扭曲了的窘迫時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連本應定下約定的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:47.89,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會毫無察覺地擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:55.51,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始崩壞但曾經互相理解的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:57.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其撇下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:02:00.76,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的末路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:05.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中不服　想與之對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:11.51,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要從當初墮落的印象中逃離開去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:16.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　就算歷經千百次也要找出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:23.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的雙眸　你手中的余溫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:28.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小聲嘟囔著「愛總是讓我遍體鱗傷…」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:33.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因畏懼堅信不疑的事而哭過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道軟弱才能變強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:39.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕堅信不疑地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:44.03,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是愛的真諦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府勢力關押設施遭到Gundam的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不爭的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是Celestial Being嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有傳言說是反政府組織自行開發了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上純屬推斷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何  這次事件是針對現政權進行恫嚇的恐怖襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了消滅反政府組織
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已決定派出直屬的治安維持部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計到Celestial Being將會復出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.29,0:00:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進而利用這點擴大了A-LAWS的權限…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的想法？還是吠陀的推算？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何  快到我們出場了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.74,0:00:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李維夫·李拜巴爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加蒂斯薩已經出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦下達出擊命令  立刻就能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:00:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到這種程度  李拜巴爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次作戰已經拜託給某人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是迪拜因嗎？還是布林格？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通人類而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但某種程度上已經超出常人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:54.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#05 故國在燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留守可真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要修復普特利麥奧斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驗證A-LAWS新型MS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有調試OO的Twin-Drive系統等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做的事多著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道  發發牢騷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:16.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}魯卜哈利沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:16.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（阿拉伯半島南部大沙漠，不毛之地東部是石油產地）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在這樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得聯邦沒發現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦在非加盟國居多的中東全境散佈了GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對外宣稱通過散佈粒子能阻斷恐怖組織的信息交流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際目的是使中東各國的經濟處於癱瘓狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不依照聯邦政策做的國家就沒好果子吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也多虧了GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆的設施沒被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞭解得還真詳細
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬於常識範疇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得到嗎  已確認你方機體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正打開艙門中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是拯救了阿扎提斯坦的英雄機體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正是時候 　Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我們見見廬山真面目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須保守機密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼見外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟受了人家恩惠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府組織  卡塔隆…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你們同意此次會談
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡塔隆中東支部的克勞斯·格拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是Celestial Being…自我介紹就免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們理解你們的苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你們救出了瑪麗娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後將由我們付起保護的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想留在Celestial Being嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是…怎麼會加入反政府組織…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請拜託你們保護一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·克洛斯羅德  他是平民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無端地被A-LAWS懷疑是卡塔隆戰鬥員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓你受委屈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會盡責保護他的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…別擅自…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不能隨便進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把他們撫養成卡塔隆的戰鬥員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是把舉目無親的孩子保護起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦私自進行的中東政策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其危害便以這種形式表現了出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由於資金有限  無法收容所有的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是瑪麗娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也認識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  是瑪麗娜大人本人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜殿下  你能陪陪孩子們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎  那到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要  我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果真是皇族的象徵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該進入正題了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們卡塔隆為了推翻現聯邦政權…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉  我們並不像貴組織擁有政治目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你們正與聯邦對立
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的敵人不是聯邦政府  而是A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道打擊政府直屬的獨立部隊與我們的目的相違背嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕為了討伐A-LAWS的惡行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也應該互相協作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我直言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡所擁有的MS對抗搭載了GN-Drive的型號簡直不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也希望能夠協助你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是補給或是裝備也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想盡一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:14.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}波斯灣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損失了Trilobite真是失態啊 　少校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻我顏面無存
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬內金上校  你與少校一同指揮部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們A-LAWS是聯邦的盾  也是聯邦的矛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不允許失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是如此  下一次也聽從我的指令行事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧  Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕難從命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有司令部下達的獨自行動的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是One-man Army
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一人編制的軍隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能擅自就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經說過我獲得許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校也出擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給了我一支部隊負責搜索Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到正規軍竟淪落到A-LAWS的侍從…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  他還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指安德烈少尉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他工作很賣力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說真是諷刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從心底裡恨著我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我披上軍裝的時候起  就已不再是他的父親了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  我打算…同意那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做上校養女的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次見面與您詳談
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個幸福的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜大人  還有這個還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要等一會了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來這邊玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子也是你們的犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了被你們改變世界的犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你麻木到什麼都感覺不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也無法融入那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然明白這點  為什麼還要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自有我的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒打算讓你瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算恨我也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前  請聽我唯一的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然拉攏Celestial Being的可能性很小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  有那個回答就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與A-LAWS戰鬥會十分慘烈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久的將來  雙方必然迎來合作的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧  GIN1
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們想閒談到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回到自己崗位上工作去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會談結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但多了一份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾送到阿扎提斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我如此任性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不能用Gundam啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一被發現了  會殃及到阿扎提斯坦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我用這架機體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Gundam送回托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  你也不用回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這4年到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然會開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是Celestial Being還是卡塔隆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是引發戰爭的罪魁禍首
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能待在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Celestial Being的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上有我的朋友  想見見他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡去鎮上太遠了  開車去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到瑪麗娜公主了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛還跟Celestial Being在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他們在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam將返回母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開艙門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個能穿越沙漠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會用這種輕裝甲在沙漠中穿行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我查過泛用標準資料  這人是卡塔隆成員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！不是這樣的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少扯謊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼粗魯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上…上校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下  由我來問話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是戰士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常年在軍中所以能看出來  你沒有戰鬥者的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是說  你不是卡塔隆的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該是跟Celestial Being一起行動的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從資料上來看  你幾個月前還在曾出現過Gundam的普勞德從事衛星開發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你還出現在這個昨天與Gundam交戰過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  這只是簡單的推理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…既不屬於卡塔隆也不屬於Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  我只是想問你些問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會為難你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能刪除關於我的資料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會斟酌的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四中隊  巴拉克·基寧上尉等五人前來報到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  屬實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻發送指令書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個天真的女人太怕事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個好消息  司令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現卡塔隆的軍事基地了  有Gundam在的概率也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上應對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令  也請給我們出擊許可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強了  你們休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明Gundam就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這指令書是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然說把自動機器人開到殲滅模式投入使用…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒道理  這種非人道的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  上層的命令是絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對於這作戰內容就無動於衷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  對方是反政府勢力  無須同情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種作戰…我終於明白上校反對我調動的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯密爾諾夫上校是個為了任務可以犧牲血親的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲血親？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人曾對我母親見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  A-LAWS找到反政府組織的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  由我來聯絡特瑞亞他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這蠢貨！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你向A-LAWS報告了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這就是我們的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行判斷的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛斯羅德  你現在趕快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的存在被A-LAWS知道了  他們是淩駕於法律之上的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的權限無法保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在被知道了  難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美發來了緊急暗號通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像A-LAWS的MS隊正在前往卡塔隆的設施  我們怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往救援  托勒密  展開對衛星光學迷彩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急上浮  準備發射Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密  開始緊急上浮  離海面還有0043
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被A-LAWS找到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡還有孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快  趕快啊  可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現A-LAWS的MS隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來攻擊這裡了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人數量多少！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底情報是從哪裡漏出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘快把孩子們帶到避難所去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯  我們出擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰力相差太懸殊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是堅守這裡  等待Celestial Being的救援為好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟炸嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認到疑似敵人基地的建築物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用那種舊式的MS…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行對敵人基地的掃蕩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射出自動機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動機器人  射出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍用自動機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  快躲避！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來晚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆的各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快啊  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩麗絲機  迎擊先行的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了…瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那動作…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機  迎擊Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道  為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全無興致！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…這種事是人做的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以無人兵器進行虐殺…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然連扳機都不自己扣下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還有絲毫的罪惡感嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙管火箭炮  轟炸模式！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初期目的已達成  撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕  饒不了你們  A-LAWS！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別逃啊  別逃啊  A-LAWS！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…A-LAWS…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  這就是我們的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是超兵  是為了戰鬥而存在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.31,0:21:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我妄想著要得到常人的幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是對我的懲罰嗎  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都…都怪我…都怪我說出來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的！
