Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…阿扎提斯坦…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這規模  不是恐怖襲擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…那顏色…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是！
